trans-unit.source: Provides an object model that allows you to construct activities dynamically that interface with the WF designer and runtime using <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ICustomTypeDescriptor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um modelo de objeto que lhe permite construir atividades dinamicamente esse interface com o designer WF e, em seguida, utilizar o runtime <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ICustomTypeDescriptor"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.DynamicActivity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Activities.DynamicActivity"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: With <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity> you can create new activities without creating new types.
trans-unit.target: Com <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>pode criar novas atividades sem criar novos tipos de.</xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity> with its associated XAML support in <xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices> allows new arguments to be defined in XAML and bound by the host without requiring XAML to be compiled.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>com o respetivo suporte XAML associado no <xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices>permite argumentos novo a ser definido em XAML e vinculado ao anfitrião sem necessidade de XAML a ser compilada.</xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices></xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>
